<font color="red" size="3">Overview</font>

Community Applications is a plugin designed to make finding, installing, and managing docker and plugin applications.  When using this plugin, there is no longer any need to use the <em>Repositories</em> section of the Docker Tab

From top to bottom will explain all aspects of Community Applications starting from the basic and going to the more advanced options.

All items within this plugin have tooltips enabled to further guide you in operation.  For a help for the settings for this plugin, load the settings page and press Help.  Each item will have associated help text displayed.

After installation, a new tab will appear on unRaid's main menu called "Apps".  Additionally, there will be a section within the Settings tab called Community Applications which has some extra utilities to customize the operation of this plugin.
