<font color="red" size="3">Technical Stuff</font>

Community Applications (and its predecessor Community Repositories) introduced a number of additional XML tags in order to perform it's magic.  Any application / template author and/or maintainer should check out the list of schema additions here:  <a href='http://lime-technology.com/forum/index.php?topic=40299.0' target='_blank'>http://lime-technology.com/forum/index.php?topic=40299.0</a>

Depending upon which browser you are using, there may be a slight delay (~1-2 seconds) in displaying the results (in particular, All Applications using Table mode).  Some browsers are faster than others are sorting out all the displayed information.  In my testing, on a PC, Chrome is by far the fastest at rendering the results.  Note that generally whenever CA searches or re-renders the display, a spinning ring will appear.  <strong>When that ring stops spinning, CA has finished, and any delays from that point onwards are 100% entirely due to your browser</strong>


